data.name: sqlSelectCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT c.KnownAs, l.Level_ID, l.Level_Description, a.Response, a.Response_Time, a.Response_Notes FROM WF_Route AS h INNER JOIN WF_RouteDet AS a ON a.WF_Route_ID = h.WF_Route_ID INNER JOIN web_strike_test.dbo.Contact AS c ON c.ID = a.Contact_ID INNER JOIN web_strike_test.dbo.WS_Approval_Levels AS l ON l.Approval_Level_ID = a.Approval_Level_ID WHERE h.WF_Route_ID=@WF_Route_ID ORDER BY l.Level_ID, c.KnownAs

data.name: sqlSelectCommand2.CommandText
data.value: select p.po_id, p.pri_num, p.po, p.order_date, p.org_due_date, p.supplier, t.DESCRIPTION AS POType, st.Description AS POSupplyType, s.name, p.po_add1, p.po_add2, p.po_city, p.po_state, p.po_zip, c.DESCRIPTION AS Country, cast(ph.pri_code as varchar(15)) + ' - '+ph.pri_name [Project], isnull((select SUM(ISNULL(d.extension,0)) from PO_DETAIL d where d.po_id=p.po_id),0) [PurchaseAmount], ISNULL(p.HOLD_AMT,0) [HOLD_AMT], p.ContractPO_Start_Date, p.ContractPO_End_Date, cst.SubType_Description from PO_HEADER p left outer join SUPPLIER_MASTER s on s.SUPPLIER=p.supplier left outer join COUNTRIES AS c ON c.COUNTRY_ID = p.po_country_id left outer join PO_TYPE AS t ON t.TYPE = p.po_type left outer join PO_SupplyType AS st ON st.PO_SupplyType_ID = p.po_supplytype_id left outer join PROJ_HEADER ph on ph.pri_id=p.pri_num left outer join PO_ContractPO_SubType cst on cst.id=p.ContractPO_Subtype_ID where p.po_id=@po_id

data.name: sqlSelectCommand3.CommandText
data.value: select d.part_no_desc, d.qty_ordered, u.DESCRIPTION AS UnitOfMeasure, d.unit_price AS Amount, d.extension AS Total, d.reference, d.PART_NO_EXT_DESC, d.PO_DETAIL_ID from po_detail as d LEFT OUTER JOIN UNITS_OF_MEASURE AS u ON u.UNIT_OF_MEASURE_CODE = d.uom where (d.po_id = @po_id)

data.name: sqlSelectCommand4.CommandText
data.value: SELECT REVISION_ID, PO_ID, PO_DETAIL_ID, USERNAME, REVISION_NUMBER, REVISION_TYPE, REVISION_DATE, PARTNO, PARTDESC, QUANTITY, UOM, ALT_UOM_USED, CONVERTED_QTY, CONVERTED_UNIT_PRICE, UNIT_PRICE, EXTENSION, Est_ID, CO_Num, CO_Desc FROM PO_DETAIL_REVISIONS WHERE (PO_DETAIL_ID = @po_detail_id)
